column3: Traffic Alert for Parkers Mill Rd:
column4: Update:  Parkers Mill Rd is now open at Dedman Ln.  Access to Parkers Mill Rd from Versailles Rd (near the Woodford Co line) remains blocked as Police work to clear a serious collision.
Wednesday March 15 thru Saturday March 18 at Rupp Arena.
Expect increased congestion if traveling downtown.
Use added caution and watch for pedestrians.
